text: Pekka Alanen (born 14 July 1945) is a Finnish wrestler. He competed at the 1964 Summer Olympics and the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1945 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Finland Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:People from Lappajärvi
